        {
            "title": "貝萊德私募信貸部門再遭打擊 2500萬美元貸款三個月內由面值歸零",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 僅僅只過了三個月，<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:貝萊德;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/貝萊德\">貝萊德</a>公司就將一筆其評估認為與面值等價的私募貸款估值減記到零，這是該行私募信貸部門近期遭遇的第二次突發性資產減記。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">貝萊德TCP資本公司在上周發布的第四季度財報中報告稱，向Infinite Commerce Holdings提供的約2500萬美元貸款目前已毫無價值。該基金曾在第三季度將這筆次級債務的價值定為與面值同等。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">貝萊德一位代表拒絕置評。記者暫未與Infinite Commerce的發言人取得聯繫。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-8297cc08-0127-3be4-b42a-7bdab55405c9-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">雖然這只是一個陷入困境的細分領域中的一筆小額貸款，但突如其來的減值突顯了批評者所描述的私募信貸領域一個關鍵斷層：非流動性貸款的估值與這些貸款背後企業的業績惡化存在時間上的滯後。Zips Car Wash在尋求破產保護前的幾個月裡，其私募信貸支持者給出的貸款估值仍接近面值。去年11月，貝萊德TCP對其向陷入困境的家居裝修公司Renovo Home Partners提供的貸款進行了全額減記。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">財報顯示，Infinite Commerce的另一家貸款機構Victory Park在12月31日也對其頭寸進行了全額減記，並將業績不佳歸咎於需求疲軟和關稅導致的庫存成本上升。Victory Park的代表暫未回應置評請求。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">根據第四季度財報，貝萊德TCP還對其在SellerX的頭寸進行了部分減記。該基金上周將股息從每股25美分削減至17美分。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題BlackRock Slashes Another Private Loan Value From 100 to Zero</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%B2%9D%E8%90%8A%E5%BE%B7%E7%A7%81%E5%8B%9F%E4%BF%A1%E8%B2%B8%E9%83%A8%E9%96%80%E5%86%8D%E9%81%AD%E6%89%93%E6%93%8A-2500%E8%90%AC%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%83%E8%B2%B8%E6%AC%BE%E4%B8%89%E5%80%8B%E6%9C%88%E5%85%A7%E7%94%B1%E9%9D%A2%E5%80%BC%E6%AD%B8%E9%9B%B6-150957249.html",
