        {
            "title": "受伊朗衝突影響 歐盟3月底財長會議不再按原計畫舉行",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 據一名<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:塞浦路斯;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/塞浦路斯\">塞浦路斯</a>官員透露，原定於3月底在塞浦路斯舉行的歐盟財長非正式會議將不再按原計畫舉行。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這位官員表示：「所有原定於3月在塞浦路斯舉行的會議，要麼將以線上形式舉行，要麼將重新安排時間。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">其中包括原定於3月27日至28日在塞浦路斯首都尼科西亞舉行的歐盟財長和央行行長會議。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該官員表示，作出這一決定的原因是「航班連接出現部分擾動」，並強調此舉旨在提高「可預見性」，避免給各代表團帶來不便。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">塞浦路斯目前擔任歐盟輪值主席國，為期六個月，任期至6月結束。該國境內設有一處英國空軍基地，該基地於周日晚間遭無人機襲擊，這是首次針對歐洲領土的攻擊。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-0d5cf18b-5941-3174-a40f-a6b9bc9268da-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Cyprus Meeting of EU Finance Chiefs Postponed on Iran War</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%8F%97%E4%BC%8A%E6%9C%97%E8%A1%9D%E7%AA%81%E5%BD%B1%E9%9F%BF-%E6%AD%90%E7%9B%9F3%E6%9C%88%E5%BA%95%E8%B2%A1%E9%95%B7%E6%9C%83%E8%AD%B0%E4%B8%8D%E5%86%8D%E6%8C%89%E5%8E%9F%E8%A8%88%E7%95%AB%E8%88%89%E8%A1%8C-142646981.html",
